<p>
This video shows chef Kin Jing Mark making Chinese hand-pulled noodles.
He held the Guinness World Record as the fastest human noodle 
maker for several consecutive years. His last record was set in 1993 on 
NBC's afternoon talk show, <i>Vicki</i>, when he stretched out 4,096 strings of Chinese noodles by hand in 41.34 seconds.
The fine noodles are called dragon beard noodles (longxu mian).
</p>

<div class="center">
<!-- Alton Brown - Making noodles by hand -->
